{"4594450": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Futa Heim", "steam_appid": 4594450, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4594450/extras/8d882d1cb47c2f13cbd8cbfdc55daa99.avif?t=1776618749\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4594450/extras_big/8d882d1cb47c2f13cbd8cbfdc55daa99.avif?t=1776618749 width=1560 height=678 /></span><br><strong>世界與衝突</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>都市奇幻</strong> 背景充滿精靈、吸血鬼、魅魔、變形者、合成體及其他奇異物種，多個世界由傳送門/蟲洞相互連通。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>權力結構 </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雌性精靈掌控一切，她們他媽的恨透了扶她，原因如下：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扶她將其他扶她繁殖進精靈的逼裡，擴張她們的種群</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扶她與雄性精靈交配產出價值連城的魔法蛋</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一個扶她的存在都威脅著她們的掌控，奪走她們的丈夫，斷絕她們的血脈</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4594450/extras/1f6d4079dce2c8e4a0980af8ef8cd6e3.avif?t=1776618749\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4594450/extras_big/1f6d4079dce2c8e4a0980af8ef8cd6e3.avif?t=1776618749 width=1560 height=678 /></span>她們的對策？ <strong>扶她解剖研究所</strong> —— 一所訓練獵人跨世界捕獲扶她、進行實驗以使其精液失效的學院。不再繁殖，不再產蛋，不再威脅。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你的角色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're <strong>Dromazeth Throxxa</strong>，一名效力於扶她邪教的女吸血鬼，該邪教名為 <strong>Futhorix Cabal</strong>。你潛入研究所，偽裝成一名&quot;訓練靶&quot;扶她，而實際上你在：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立你自己的繁育後宮（雄性、雌性、其他扶她）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生產並出售魔法蛋牟利</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >為邪教招募精靈皇族</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >密謀推翻整個精靈帝國</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img cla